Package: bayesmetaipd
Title: Bayesian Random-Effects Meta-Analysis for IPD (Logistic)
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Yuan", "Zhou", email = "yuanzhouu@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits a Bayesian hierarchical random-effects meta-analysis model
    using individual participant data (IPD) with a logistic observation model.
    Default settings reproduce the Simulation Study 2 Benchmark results from
    Kim et al. (Bayesian-Meta supplementary materials).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    mvtnorm,
    MCMCpack,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
